## Artifact 3 â€” Plan 11-08's proposed C++ composition (verbatim from Task 3 Â§action item 3)

```cpp
// In Direct3d11_StateCache.cpp â€” file-scope shadows + the WVP composition

static XMFLOAT4X4 s_cachedView;     // set in setWorldToCameraTransform
static XMFLOAT4X4 s_cachedProj;     // set in setProjectionMatrix
static XMFLOAT4X4 s_cachedWorld;    // set in setObjectToWorldTransformAndScale

void setObjectToWorldTransformAndScale(const Transform &transform, const Vector &scale)
{
  // ... shadow s_cachedWorld from transform.getMatrix() + apply scale to basis columns ...

  XMMATRIX V = XMLoadFloat4x4(&s_cachedView);
  XMMATRIX P = XMLoadFloat4x4(&s_cachedProj);
  XMMATRIX W = XMLoadFloat4x4(&s_cachedWorld);

  XMMATRIX wtp = XMMatrixMultiply(P, V);    // mirror line 3359 D3DXMatrixMultiply(out, P, V)
  XMMATRIX wvp = XMMatrixMultiply(wtp, W);  // mirror line 4034 D3DXMatrixMultiply(out, WTP, W)

  Direct3d11_VertexSlot0CB cb;
  XMStoreFloat4x4(&cb.objectWorldCameraProjectionMatrix, wvp);
  XMStoreFloat4x4(&cb.objectWorldMatrix, W);
  // ... fill remaining 896 bytes of cb with initial-state defaults ...

  Direct3d11_ConstantBuffer::updateVS(0, &cb, sizeof(cb));
}
```

The cbuffer struct `Direct3d11_VertexSlot0CB` is C++-side, mirroring the shader's `SwgVertexConstants` cbuffer.

