747:	// Rule D (Iter-13): structural cbuffer wrap.
748-	//
749-	// Detects a contiguous run of GLOBAL declarations with `: register(cN)`
750-	// bindings and wraps them in an explicit cbuffer block, converting each
751-	// `register(cN)` to `packoffset(cN)`. Sidesteps the FXC X4016
752-	// "overlapping register semantics not yet implemented 'c0'" rejection
753-	// that fires when D3D9-era explicit register bindings sit at file scope
754-	// and get auto-promoted to the implicit $Globals cbuffer under SM4+ /
755-	// vs_4_0_level_9_3 even with BACKWARDS_COMPATIBILITY enabled.
756-	//
